    </files>
  </knowledge>

  <steps>
    <step order="1">Identify every data-fetching call in SmartTodo Code Page (likely a hook or service file).</step>
    <step order="2">Replace `sprk_event?$filter=sprk_todoflag eq true` with `sprk_todos` queries; preserve attribute selection and ordering logic.</step>
    <step order="3">Update column/card rendering to use `sprk_todo`-prefixed attribute names where they differ from the prior shape.</step>
    <step order="4">Remove any `sprk_event` imports / type definitions from the kanban path.</step>
    <step order="5">Run `npm run build` + `npm test`. Verify clean build + test pass.</step>
    <step order="6">Capture a browser network trace while loading the kanban; verify only `sprk_todos` requests from the kanban path.</step>
    <step order="7">Fluent v9 lint pass on changed files.</step>
    <step order="8">Update TASK-INDEX.md status to ✅ completed.</step>
  </steps>

  <tools>
